HEADWORD: Futurition
<hw>Fu`tu*ri"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>futurition</ets>.]</ety> <def>The state of being future;
futurity.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Nothing . . . can have this imagined <qex>futurition</qex>, but as
it is decreed.</q> <rj><qau>Coleridge.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Futurity</ent>⟦br⟧
